      "writtenOn": "2026-04-16T23:19:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Have to solve Ed\u0027s comment below first but do you need /redfish/v1/schema here? \n\nI don\u0027t think \nurl.starts_with(\"/redfish/v1/schema/\") returns true when /redfish/v1/schema",
